aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWPnC_ItemRuleEngine) (Def Version:3) (Implem Version:1)
uses aWFRuleDesc, WFTypes
type tWF___RateCategory : (A_, A, B, C, D)
function EmergencyMedicalInsuranceA_(NumberofUsers : Int4, Age : Int4) return Num8 uses aWFStandAloneRule
var tmpRule : aWFRuleDesc
tmpRule = self.GetExactRuleToExecuteFromRankInRuleDesc(0, self.CurrentDate) if tmpRule <> Nil aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(NumberofUsers, 0, tmpRule) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(Age, 1, tmpRule) tmpRule.GetStandAloneResult(_Result, self) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).CleanParamsAfterExecution(tmpRule) else self.AppendComment('No rule version defined at this date') endIf endFunc
function EmergencyMedicalInsuranceA(NumberofDays : Int4, Age : Int4) return Num8 uses aWFStandAloneRule
var tmpRule : aWFRuleDesc
tmpRule = self.GetExactRuleToExecuteFromRankInRuleDesc(1, self.CurrentDate) if tmpRule <> Nil aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(NumberofDays, 0, tmpRule) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(Age, 1, tmpRule) tmpRule.GetStandAloneResult(_Result, self) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).CleanParamsAfterExecution(tmpRule) else self.AppendComment('No rule version defined at this date') endIf endFunc
function EmergencyMedicalInsuranceB(NumberofDays : Int4, Age : Int4) return Num8 uses aWFStandAloneRule
var tmpRule : aWFRuleDesc
tmpRule = self.GetExactRuleToExecuteFromRankInRuleDesc(2, self.CurrentDate) if tmpRule <> Nil aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(NumberofDays, 0, tmpRule) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(Age, 1, tmpRule) tmpRule.GetStandAloneResult(_Result, self) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).CleanParamsAfterExecution(tmpRule) else self.AppendComment('No rule version defined at this date') endIf endFunc
function EmergencyMedicalInsuranceC(NumberofDays : Int4, Age : Int4) return Num8 uses aWFStandAloneRule
var tmpRule : aWFRuleDesc
tmpRule = self.GetExactRuleToExecuteFromRankInRuleDesc(3, self.CurrentDate) if tmpRule <> Nil aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(NumberofDays, 0, tmpRule) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(Age, 1, tmpRule) tmpRule.GetStandAloneResult(_Result, self) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).CleanParamsAfterExecution(tmpRule) else self.AppendComment('No rule version defined at this date') endIf endFunc
function EmergencyMedicalInsuranceD(Age : Int4) return Num8 uses aWFStandAloneRule
var tmpRule : aWFRuleDesc
tmpRule = self.GetExactRuleToExecuteFromRankInRuleDesc(4, self.CurrentDate) if tmpRule <> Nil aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(Age, 0, tmpRule) tmpRule.GetStandAloneResult(_Result, self) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).CleanParamsAfterExecution(tmpRule) else self.AppendComment('No rule version defined at this date') endIf endFunc
function Item__RateCategory return tWF___RateCategory type tpValue : .tWF___RateCategory
var p : tWF___RateCategory
if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(5, 8, 'Item__RateCategory') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
function Item__NumberofTravelDays return Int4 type tpValue : .Int4
var p : Int4
if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(6, 8, 'Item__NumberofTravelDays') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
function Item__Age return Int4 type tpValue : .Int4
var p : Int4
if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(7, 8, 'Item__Age') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : tWFNum8) switch self.Item__RateCategory when A_ Result = self.EmergencyMedicalInsuranceA_(self.Item__NumberofTravelDays, self.Item__Age) * self.Item__NumberofTravelDays self.AppendBillLineDetail(Result, Concat('Daily table rate A and ', self.Item__Age)) endWhen when A Result = self.EmergencyMedicalInsuranceA(self.Item__NumberofTravelDays, self.Item__Age) * self.Item__NumberofTravelDays endWhen when B Result = self.EmergencyMedicalInsuranceB(self.Item__NumberofTravelDays, self.Item__Age) * self.Item__NumberofTravelDays endWhen when C Result = self.EmergencyMedicalInsuranceC(self.Item__NumberofTravelDays, self.Item__Age) * self.Item__NumberofTravelDays endWhen when D Result = self.EmergencyMedicalInsuranceD(self.Item__Age) * self.Item__NumberofTravelDays endWhen endSwitch endProc

aWPnC_OfferedService.Description: {\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fswiss\fcharset0 Frutiger-Cn;}{\f1\fnil\fcharset0 Frutiger-Cn;}{\f2\fnil MS Sans Serif;}} {\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue0;} \viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1033\f0\fs20 Trip Interruption Insurance is an optional plan that provides \par coverage for an individual trip whether you have purchased \par the single-trip plan or the multi-trip plan. If your trip is \par interrupted due to a covered event that occurs after the day \par you leave home, under this insurance, we will pay up to a \par maximum of \cf1\b\f1 $1,500 for single coverage\cf0\b0\f0 , or $5,000 for family \par coverage for: \par \par 1. a) the prepaid portion of your trip that is non-refundable \par and non-transferable to another travel date, except \par prepaid unused transportation home ; or \par b) your additional and unplanned hotel and meal \par expenses, your essential phone calls and taxi fares \par to a maximum of up to $300 per day for up to \par 2 days when no earlier transportation arrangements \par are available; and/or \par c) \cf1\b\f1\fs16 your one-way economy class airfare via the most \par cost-effective itinerary to return you home.\fs12 \par \cf0\b0\f0\fs16 \par \cf1\ul\f1\fs20 2. Events covered after you arrive in Canada from \par home include:\cf0\ulnone\f0 \par a) your or your travel companion's medical condition or \par death; \par b) your or your travel companion's immediate family \par member's medical condition, or death; \par c) \cf1\b\f1 emergency hospitalization or death of the person \par whose guest you are during your trip.\cf0\b0\f0 \par \fs24 \par \cf1\f2\fs16 \par }
aWPnC_OfferedService.Name: Trip Interruption Coverage

aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWPnC_ItemRuleEngine) (Def Version:3) (Implem Version:1)
uses WFTypes
function Item__NumberofTravelDays return Int4 type tpValue : .Int4
var p : Int4
if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(0, 8, 'Item__NumberofTravelDays') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : tWFNum8) var BaseAmount : Num8
BaseAmount = 25 self.AppendComment(Concat('Base Amount:', BaseAmount)) if self.Item__NumberofTravelDays <= 10 Result = BaseAmount else Result = (self.Item__NumberofTravelDays - 25) * 0.1 + BaseAmount endIf endProc
aWFRuleDesc.Name: r3

aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWPnC_ItemRuleEngine) (Def Version:3) (Implem Version:1)
uses WFTypes
function Item__NumberofBags return Int4 type tpValue : .Int4
var p : Int4
if self.EvaluateFieldDescFromRank(0, 8, 'Item__NumberofBags') p = tpValue(self.pFieldValue). _Result = p endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : tWFNum8) var BaseAmount : Num8
BaseAmount = 20 self.AppendComment(Concat('Base Amount:', BaseAmount)) Result = self.Item__NumberofBags * 5 + BaseAmount endProc
